Task 2: Absolute and Relative Paths

The starting  is /home/joyous.

1.Command 1: cd ..        //Puts us in the home directory.
2.Command 2: touch exercise.md 

Desktop    Downloads    Music     Public     Videos
Documents  exercise.md  Pictures  Templates  workspace
 
3.Command 3: mv exercise.md /tmp     //Moves file to /tmp
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:/tmp$ ls
config-err-xlXvEY
exercise.md

4.Command 4: rm /tmp/exercise.md        //deletes  file
 without having to change directories (using absolute pathname)
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:/tmp$ ls
config-err-xlXvEY

