Task 4: The locate command

# 1: find / -name umuzi*

joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ find / -name umuzi*
/home/joyous/umuzi.md,

# 2: find / -name umuzi* > search_result.md

joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ ls
cohort.md  Downloads  Public            summary.md  Videos
Desktop    Music      recruit.md,       Templates   workspace

Documents  Pictures   search_result.md  umuzi.md,

joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ cat search_result.md
/home/joyous/umuzi.md,


