Task 5:

1.Command 1: cd Documents 
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ cd Documents

2.Command 2: mkdir myDocument
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Documents$ mkdir myDocument
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Documents$ cd myDocument
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Documents/myDocument$ touch pad.md
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Documents/myDocument$ ls
pad.md

3.Command 3: cd ..

4.Command 4: cd Desktop
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ cd Desktop

5.Command 5: mkdir Work
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Desktop$ mkdir Work


6.Command 6: cd Work

7.Command 7: cp /home/joyous/Documents/pad.md ./pad_copy.md
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~/Desktop/Work$ cp /home/joyous/Documents/myDocument/pad.md ./pad_copy.md

8.Command 8: locate updatedb
9.Command 9: cd -
10.Command 10: find /home/joyous/Desktop/ -name pad*
joyous@joyous-Mecer-X102:~$ find /home/joyous/Desktop/ -name pad*
/home/joyous/Desktop/Work/pad_copy.md


